repository-code: "https://github.com/coodawy/AMD-Detection-Tool"
url: "https://www.climtawy.com"
abstract: >
  Automated detection and mapping system for acid mine drainage (AMD) and iron sulfate
  minerals using Landsat 8/9 and Sentinel-2 satellite imagery. Extends USGS terrestrial
  mineral detection methodology (Rockwell et al., 2021) to contaminated water bodies.
  Implements multi-criteria water quality scoring (0-7 points) combining spectral indices
  for large-scale environmental monitoring. Open-source Google Earth Engine implementation
  enabling cost-effective watershed assessment worldwide.
